OL,3,CSon of Mango fashion brand founder
OL,4,Carrested over father's death
OL,6,FSpanish police have arrested the son
OL,7,Fof Isak Andic, the founder of the
OL,8,Ffashion brand Mango, for allegedly
OL,9,Fplaying a role in his death.
OL,11,FThe 71-year-old billionaire was hiking
OL,12,Fwith his son in the mountains near
OL,13,FBarcelona, when he fell about 150
OL,14,Fmetres (500 feet) down a cliff and
OL,15,Fdied, in November 2024.
OL,17,FHis son Jonathan Andic, aged 45, was
OL,18,Fthe only witness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
