OL,3,CSon of Mango fashion brand founder
OL,4,Carrested over father's death
OL,6,FJonathan is the eldest of Isak Andic's
OL,7,Fthree children and one of his father's
OL,8,Fheirs. He is the vice chairman of the
OL,9,Fboard at Mango, one of Spain's biggest
OL,10,Fretailers.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
