OL,3,CSon of Mango fashion brand founder
OL,4,Carrested over father's death
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Mossos d'Esquadra,
OL,7,Fthe Catalan regional police, said that
OL,8,FJonathan Andic was taken to court
OL,9,Ffacilities in Martorell, a city in
OL,10,Feastern Spain where the case is being
OL,11,Finvestigated.
OL,13,FThe case is subject to a nondisclosure
OL,14,Forder, he added.
OL,16,FPolice opened an investigation at the
OL,17,Ftime, but it was closed after a few
OL,18,Fweeks. It was reopened in March 2025,
OL,19,Fand in October police confirmed the
OL,20,Fdeath was being investigated as a
OL,21,Fpossible homicide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
