OL,3,CSon of Mango fashion brand founder
OL,4,Carrested over father's death
OL,6,FMango has 2,900 stores in 120 markets
OL,7,Faround the world. The fashion group's
OL,8,Frevenue hit a record high of nearly
OL,9,F3.8 billion euros (4.4 billion
OL,10,Fdollars) in 2025, an 11% increase from
OL,11,Fthe previous year.
